IMAPAccount dmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User derekyoungmath@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.password-store/passnew.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore dmail-remote
Account dmail

MaildirStore dmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.Mail/dmail/
Inbox ~/.Mail/dmail/Inbox

Channel sync-dmail-default
Far :dmail-remote:
Near :dmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Near

Channel sync-dmail-sent
Far :dmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :dmail-local:sent
Create Near

IMAPAccount family
Host imap.gmail.com
User dowewas8@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.password-store/common.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore family-remote
Account family

MaildirStore family-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.Mail/family/
Inbox ~/.Mail/family/Inbox/

Channel family-default
Far :family-remote:
Near :family-local:Inbox
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel family-sent
Far :family-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :family-local:Sent
Create Both
SyncState *

Group dmail
Channel sync-dmail-default
Channel sync-dmail-sent

Group family
Channel family-default
Channel family-sent
